\description{
\code{clade} provides agent-based simulations of evolution, foraging ecology,
and social behaviour. The R layer is an interface; the per-tick
simulation kernel runs in Julia via \link[JuliaConnectoR:juliaEval]{JuliaConnectoR},
so the R↔Julia boundary is crossed exactly once per \code{\link[=run_alife]{run_alife()}} call.
}
